| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4657 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 199cd104-dc63-558b-88eb-bfe09058e110"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
